    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 18 years

          -  Suitable for intra-arterial treatment for acute stroke up to 8 hours from onset of
             symptoms

          -  Clinical equipoise for best mode of sedation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any known allergy to either proposed medication and its alternative

          -  Any patient that has been intubated prior to randomization

          -  Posterior circulation strokes

          -  Age ≤ 18

          -  Pregnant female
      </textblock>
